{"tid":1465172,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"想贏嘅同我入撚曬嚟","createTime":"2019-08-13T15:51:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T16:27:42.000Z","uid":207418,"like":28,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b98c44861c018d7ec5c8e7d067a22e707440d005","tid":1465172,"uid":207418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:51:24.000Z","msg":"我覺得818大遊行嘅遊行路線可以由香港站或東涌站<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">行去機場</span></span><br />\n<br />\n鑑於小妹尋日去機場誤信未FC嘅散水消息，我同fd一齊好早走咗，仲因為等唔到巴士又逼唔到機鐵所以就跟大隊行路出東涌站，on99咁行咗大概一個鐘，沿途風景都唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋終點喺機場嘅話，可以順便和你飛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家又可以喺機場涼下冷氣食下嘢休息下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因為行馬路嘅關係，有機會會唔覺意變左巴士不合作運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n終點站為機場嘅好處：<br />\n1.<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">慳錢</span></span><br />\n大家可以搭巴士或狗鐵去東涌，唔洗搭去機場咁貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />學生哥可以慳翻少少<br />\n<br />\n2.<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">保留體力</span></span><br />\n明白各位義士平日要返工返學已經心力交瘁，但為咗出一份綿力都選擇出嚟發夢有幾攰，所以大家行完喺可以喺有冷氣嘅環境休息下之餘又做到嘢未嘗唔係一件好事<br />\n<br />\n3.<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">安全</span></span><br />\n喺機場呢個咁多遊客同記者嘅地方，班狗冇咁易亂嚟<br />\n雖然啲癲狗已經冇曬底線，但我仍然相信機場比室外安全（有錯請指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n4.<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">癱瘓機場</span></span><br />\n相信大家呢幾日有睇post都知癱瘓機場成效有幾大，我哋以最和理非嘅方法做到最多嘢，點解唔繼續做呢？而且喺機場，人多係<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">好撚重要</span></span>，等我哋一齊鏈撚爆中共春袋啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講咗咁多，唔知大家點睇呢？希望大家盡量表達意見，有錯麻煩指出，大家討論一下，睇下點樣改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：有得諗喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：咪撚on9啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">如果真係實行嘅話大家最好帶多一件黑衫去到機場換（費事臭死自己友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />），同埋例牌帶多一件衫喺機場走嗰陣換<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xjRo1Jx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxjRo1Jx.png&h=65ede11a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港最美的風景是人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"e844f3ae7d248e28408070fb2f19ca162d26ea1d","tid":1465172,"uid":207418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:51:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"49599be138f6441409489d476f701656e0bac928","tid":1465172,"uid":207418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:51:59.000Z","msg":"自推10下"},{"pid":"59ea02008f6fedf420a6729a98d8dbf41bd2b70c","tid":1465172,"uid":207418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:52:10.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"84087ce3e1eada6f876ccd0c2e72da9ae069fed0","tid":1465172,"uid":207418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:52:22.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"a9fe66bcf074ec7d2cf784d4912c7d7f9d8be58f","tid":1465172,"uid":207418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:52:32.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"b8bc2d23cf91b2343b9b121baf6029fa0d2a14bf","tid":1465172,"uid":207418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:52:44.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"d91e96d2e03a5d61e780d936087205f9cd9c467e","tid":1465172,"uid":207418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:52:54.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"a365adbadd108ef07e11c38120d20897f9d8f2f9","tid":1465172,"uid":207418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:53:04.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"96183c095c9cc8cd3279820f59bc721634454362","tid":1465172,"uid":207418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:53:14.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"9b4d38bd3fe809cdc47a3597b114c4491580c856","tid":1465172,"uid":207418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:53:31.000Z","msg":"屌 打多咗次6添"},{"pid":"2208d6a9a38a8cff400ae13e54edb38bc2249c0e","tid":1465172,"uid":207418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:53:45.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"03ed74e2c277f03ee7dd4016ca11b05f2630b0b8","tid":1465172,"uid":207418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:53:55.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"400f52d81546660a7eed233b87a9d175b8325cc2","tid":1465172,"uid":187076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:53:56.000Z","msg":"香港站係中環<br />\n中環行去機場？"},{"pid":"4664eddeebd22b24499a74bbff886a98fbe37efe","tid":1465172,"uid":281516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:55:10.000Z","msg":"[文宣] 公安單野..........<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dDChsS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dDChsS</a>"},{"pid":"9583334134e99bb4577e1010716117905713ee7e","tid":1465172,"uid":207418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"400f52d81546660a7eed233b87a9d175b8325cc2","tid":1465172,"uid":187076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:53:56.000Z","msg":"香港站係中環<br />\n中環行去機場？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:55:23.000Z","msg":"東涌站好似可行啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nsorry我唔熟嗰邊，但見到香港站同東涌站好似好近咁所以就舉埋做例<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a153cb2c66f52cbcf64cbee8fbdb321caa13858","tid":1465172,"uid":204625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:55:42.000Z","msg":"811<br />\nup"},{"pid":"7c547ea7fa2897da0b049f742383525061556e7a","tid":1465172,"uid":207418,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:55:45.000Z","msg":"負皮我都可以一齊討論阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e1e619282cf9e9e2f74eac8e06f1eed7ac94564","tid":1465172,"uid":251414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:55:51.000Z","msg":"「破解機場民意論」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1463130\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1463130</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"127908d222b82a70d5b59a3bffb76790e2f9159a","tid":1465172,"uid":207418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:56:55.000Z","msg":"我只係唔想癱瘓機場呢個成本低效益高嘅行動會因為唔夠人而失效<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4da18644d5acbab743f631c45c548c75214d02f3","tid":1465172,"uid":207418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:57:21.000Z","msg":"我好想贏阿，可唔可以大家一齊傾？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2817e1feeb1f8ec6da31e5f935d4a1b9b2a753ad","tid":1465172,"uid":52271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:57:46.000Z","msg":"香港站行入去行成日？"},{"pid":"06e86711be099067f383f7d94525dcf95f293abe","tid":1465172,"uid":92255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:58:11.000Z","msg":"其實呢一刻 未來入唔入機場<br />\n都要慢慢檢討下"},{"pid":"9a41e28f2bb34f0e0279e79d7b5844a3504c6948","tid":1465172,"uid":207418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:58:35.000Z","msg":"義士冇咗隻眼就一世，我哋癱瘓機場一時有咩用？對唔對得住佢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"678d76a2c76e73f7f9ca3f3d0af54c9fa201ee08","tid":1465172,"uid":92255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:59:25.000Z","msg":"首先 入機場撘巴士 金額其實可接受<br />\n<br />\n同埋咁樣行入機場好消耗體力 又熱<br />\n唔太認同你第二點"},{"pid":"bc4f44aaeca9c3dbe13d985926ee0db9f0e41236","tid":1465172,"uid":207418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2817e1feeb1f8ec6da31e5f935d4a1b9b2a753ad","tid":1465172,"uid":52271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:57:46.000Z","msg":"香港站行入去行成日？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:59:39.000Z","msg":"sorly 呢個我自膠咗，以為東涌站同香港站喺上下就好近<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />任屌唔嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a42e7ae8fd215a7988faefc49676f32015811ee0","tid":1465172,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:01:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2169bed6b9c78d3cf96ad6d17929d40021ad6a40","tid":1465172,"uid":207418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"678d76a2c76e73f7f9ca3f3d0af54c9fa201ee08","tid":1465172,"uid":92255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:59:25.000Z","msg":"首先 入機場撘巴士 金額其實可接受<br />\n<br />\n同埋咁樣行入機場好消耗體力 又熱<br />\n唔太認同你第二點"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:02:30.000Z","msg":"好多學生本身都已經冇乜錢，同埋咁個月係咁入機場，個數都唔細架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二點我嘅諗法就係橫掂遊行都會喺室外，而多數遊完就散水嘅做到嘅嘢唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果遊行完可以癱瘓機場就多咗個意義喺度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n多謝巴打意見，我個腦好鈍，請見諒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"877b5bdb777b8970b4b7275536b01b7a26595721","tid":1465172,"uid":207418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:02:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"72d225b945acdd070d8ff9dcd4cafe1d7aee506e","tid":1465172,"uid":52574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:03:12.000Z","msg":"從來都唔係【癱唔癱】既問題，而係【如何癱】既問題<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1464999\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1464999</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n求大家睇下同投個票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今晚係轉捩點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0eb685229ca64f83959817f29bb1f2a710e763f","tid":1465172,"uid":207418,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:03:36.000Z","msg":"係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">東涌站</span></span>作起點<br />\n打香港站嗰度我自膠咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"145257a38c987f4ae26bc5226a0b4611a216ee5f","tid":1465172,"uid":207418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:04:18.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n求下大家一齊討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"536b5c13c6ecf31e4b2ec028249ce329d60fce0a","tid":1465172,"uid":207418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:04:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b6544df2340c319e32030e80446cb884d9e15003","tid":1465172,"uid":207418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:05:18.000Z","msg":"以眼還眼 以牙還牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=